Package ch.mazluc.data

Class Table

java.lang.Object
ch.mazluc.data.Table
All Implemented Interfaces:
Data, Iterable<Object>
public class Table extends Object implements Data

Represents a table. A table is a collection of tuples. Allows to iterate through the tuples and to run some different operations on the tuples. It is an implementation of the Data interface.

Usage: 

 
 Data table = new Table();
 table.push(new Tuple(1, 2));
 table.push(new Tuple(3, 4));
 table.delete(0);
 table.push(new Tuple(5, 6));
 table.push(new Tuple(7, 8));
 table.slice(1, 2);

See Repo for more: GitHub
